This license covers SeisWork's own source code (the Python framework, web
GUI, and installer scripts) only. SeisWork orchestrates a pipeline of other
authors' seismology tools — some bundled directly in `core/src/`, most
fetched by `install.sh` from their own upstream repositories at install
time — each under its own license, listed in the License column of the
"References" table in [README.md](README.md#references).
